province_event = { 
	id = DG_Lollards.118
	title = "DG_Lollards.118.title"
	desc = "DG_Lollards.118.desc"
	picture = ANGLICAN_SERMON_eventPicture
	trigger = { 
		has_province_flag = printing_press_p
		NOT = { 
			religion_years = { 
				lollard = 50
			}
		}
		AND = { 
			continent = europe
			religion = lollard
			NOT = { 
				province_id = 2530
			}
			is_reformation_center = no
			is_island = no
			expelling_minorities = no
			development = 10
			NOT = { 
				Academia = 100
			}
			NOT = { 
				current_age = age_of_revolutions
			}
			NOT = { 
				calc_true_if = { 
					all_province = { 
						continent = europe
						religion = ROOT
						is_reformation_center = yes
					}
					amount = 3
				}
			}
			NOT = { 
				any_neighbor_province = { 
					is_reformation_center = yes
				}
			}
			NOT = { 
				any_province = { 
					superregion = PREV
					is_reformation_center = yes
					religion = lollard
				}
			}
			NOT = { 
				has_climate = tropical
			}
			NOT = { 
				has_climate = arid
			}
			NOT = { 
				has_climate = arctic
			}
			NOT = { 
				has_terrain = arctic
			}
			NOT = { 
				has_terrain = taiga
			}
			NOT = { 
				has_terrain = tundra
			}
		}
		owner = { 
			religion = lollard
		}
	}
	mean_time_to_happen = { 
		years = 5
		modifier = { 
			factor = 0.8
			owner = { 
				tag = ENG
			}
		}
		modifier = { 
			factor = 0.5
			has_province_flag = lol_craddle
		}
		modifier = { 
			factor = 0.5
			province_id = 237
		}
		modifier = { 
			factor = 0.5
			province_id = 1283
		}
		modifier = { 
			factor = 5.0
			owner = { 
				has_country_flag = accept_06
			}
		}
		modifier = { 
			factor = 10.0
			owner = { 
				has_country_flag = silence_06
			}
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = "OPT.GOOD"
		trigger = { 
			owner = { 
				religion = lollard
			}
		}
		add_reform_center = lollard
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				has_province_modifier = religious_enthusiasm
			}
			extend_province_modifier = { 
				name = religious_enthusiasm
				duration = 3650
			}
		}
		else = { 
			add_province_modifier = { 
				name = religious_enthusiasm
				duration = 3650
				hidden = yes
			}
		}
	}
	option = { 
		name = "OPT.DAMN"
		trigger = { 
			owner = { 
				NOT = { 
					religion = lollard
				}
			}
		}
		add_reform_center = lollard
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				has_province_modifier = heretic_centre
			}
			extend_province_modifier = { 
				name = heretic_centre
				duration = 3650
			}
		}
		else = { 
			add_province_modifier = { 
				name = heretic_centre
				duration = 3650
				hidden = yes
			}
		}
	}
}

	id = DG_Lollards.201
	title = "DG_Lollards.201.title"
	desc = "DG_Lollards.201.desc"
	picture = all_church_state
	hidden = yes
	trigger = { 
		is_religion_enabled = lollard
		owner = { 
			NOT = { 
				religion = lollard
			}
		}
		OR = { 
			AND = { 
				AND = { 
					is_variable_equal = { 
						which = adv
						value = 6
					}
				}
				AND = { 
					check_variable = { 
						which = jwg
						value = 1
					}
				}
			}
			AND = { 
				AND = { 
					is_variable_equal = { 
						which = adx
						value = 6
					}
				}
				AND = {

						set_variable = { 
							which = kdt
							which = ayv
						}
						multiply_variable = { 
							which = kdt
							value = 0.90
						}
						divide_variable = {

							value = 10
						}
						set_variable = {

									}
								}
							}
							subtract_variable = { 
								which = amn

									}
								}
							}
							subtract_variable = {

							add_devastation = 32
						}
						if = { 
							limit = {

									}
								}
							}
							subtract_variable = {

									}
								}
							}
							subtract_variable = {

							add_devastation = 4
						}
						if = {

										value = 2
									}
								}
							}
							subtract_variable = { 
								which = amn

							add_devastation = 2
						}
						if = {

									}
								}
							}
							subtract_variable = {

							owner = { 
								has_country_flag = lol_unrest_info

						}
						set_province_flag = mn_trauma_90
					}
				}
			}
		}
		if = { 
			limit = { 
				owner = { 
					has_country_flag = lol_unrest_info
				}
			}
			province_event = { 
				id = DG_Lollards.302
			}
		}
	}

province_event = { 
	id = DG_Lollards.302
	title = "DG_Lollards.301.title"
	desc = "DG_Lollards.301.desc"
	picture = all_church_state
	is_triggered_only = yes
	option = { 
		name = "OPT.OHNO"
		trigger_switch = { 
			on_trigger = has_province_flag
			mn_trauma_10 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_trauma_10_tt
			}
			mn_trauma_20 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_trauma_20_tt
			}
			mn_trauma_30 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_trauma_30_tt
			}
			mn_trauma_40 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_trauma_40_tt
			}
			mn_trauma_50 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_trauma_50_tt
			}
			mn_trauma_60 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_trauma_60_tt
			}
			mn_trauma_70 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_trauma_70_tt
			}
			mn_trauma_80 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_trauma_80_tt
			}
			mn_trauma_90 = { 
				custom_tooltip = mn_trauma_90_tt
			}
		}
	}
	after = { 
		hidden_effect = { 
			clr_province_flag = mn_trauma_10
			clr_province_flag = mn_trauma_20
			clr_province_flag = mn_trauma_30
			clr_province_flag = mn_trauma_40
			clr_province_flag = mn_trauma_50
			clr_province_flag = mn_trauma_60
			clr_province_flag = mn_trauma_70
			clr_province_flag = mn_trauma_80
			clr_province_flag = mn_trauma_90
		}
	}
}

province_event = { 
	id = DG_Lollards.901
	title = "DG_Lollards.901.title"
	desc = "DG_Lollards.901.desc"
	picture = all_church_state
	hidden = yes
	trigger = { 
		is_religion_enabled = protestant
		OR = { 
			AND = { 
				is_variable_equal = { 
					which = adv
					value = 6
				}
			}
			AND = { 
				is_variable_equal = { 
					which = adx
					value = 6
				}
			}
			AND = { 
				is_variable_equal = { 
					which = adz
					value = 6
				}
			}
			AND = { 
				is_variable_equal = { 
					which = aeb
					value = 6
				}
			}
			AND = { 
				is_variable_equal = { 
					which = aed
					value = 6
				}
			}
			AND = { 
				is_variable_equal = { 
					which = aef
					value = 6
				}
			}
		}
		NOT = { 
			owner = { 
				religion = lollard
			}
		}
		OR = { 
			owner = { 
				religion = protestant
			}
			owner = { 
				has_country_flag = support_02
			}
			owner = { 
				has_country_flag = accept_02
			}
		}
	}
	mean_time_to_happen = { 
		months = 300
		modifier = { 
			factor = 1.25

				religion = lollard
				stability = 3
			}
		}
		modifier = { 
			factor = 0.75
			owner = { 
				religion = lollard

					stability = -1
				}
			}

			factor = 0.75

			}

		}

					is_variable_equal = {
